narration_text: #O A man X walks in the kitchen
#C C puts the soap on the sponge scrub
#O A man X puts the bowl on the kitchen counter
#C C puts down the soap bottle
#C C puts the bowl in the sink
#C C pours the soup on the bowl
#O A man X puts the packet on the kitchen counter
#C C puts the bowl in the sink
#O A man X walks close to where C is
#O A man X takes the packet on the counter
#O A man X puts the pillow down
#C C puts down the scrub sponge
#O A man X walks close to person C
#O A man X takes the packet
#C C cleans the cup and the chop sticks
#C C puts down the chop sticks
#O A man X takes the pillow
#O A man X puts down the pillow
#C C dries his hand on the towel
#C C puts the dirt in the polythene bag
#C C puts down the polythene bag
#O A man X gives a polythene bag to C
#C C fixes the polythene bag on the sink strainer
#C C puts the sink strainer in the sink hole
#C C dries his hand on the hand towel
